Product.py¶

class job_monitoring_app.backend.app.models.product.Product(**kwargs)¶

Bases: Base, DateMixin

Represents a product, which is a device that performs computation for a study. Each product is owned by a provider.

Attributes¶

idint

Auto-generated internal product ID.

product_namestr

A name identifier given to the product.

provider_idint

The ID of the provider that owns this product.

Relationships¶

provider

The provider that this product is connected to.
